{"tid":1368093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥美娟：我冇讚過元朗鄉親做嘅嘢 譴責黃偉賢、朱凱廸失實言論","createTime":"2019-07-26T11:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:18:30.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4e77d8808a83022785cd9aca0cb70b063b7d5457","tid":1368093,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"有報道引述民主黨元朗區議員黃偉賢稱，工聯會立法會議員麥美娟曾在上星期屏山鄉事委員會的就職典禮上公開表示「<span style=\"color: red;\">元朗鄉親好嘢！前晚你哋驅趕咗啲曱甴，唔俾佢哋係元朗搞反送中嘅嘢！</span>」<br />\n<br />\n麥美娟在Facebook上載短片澄清並無發表有關言論，批評黃偉賢言論失實，完全錯誤及與事實不符，又指立法會議員朱凱廸在沒有求證下，曾先後公開轉述有關失實言論，嚴重影響個人聲譽，亦令社會分化加劇，並保留一切追究權利。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/512901462180543/videos/2311200688995368/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F512901462180543%2Fvideos%2F2311200688995368%2F&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07puyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=2c632c44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/512901462180543/videos/2311200688995368/</a>"},{"pid":"f3e199ef942864019c6ec2d171b85bffcc637cff","tid":1368093,"uid":176166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:57:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"759732ec3618e4857ac9dfa764a1ec17eb41b55b","tid":1368093,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:57:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2201824/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2201824%2F&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07puyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=7c42b88f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2201824/</a>"},{"pid":"08fa8bc63b15f847d8c13be519be76102169c080","tid":1368093,"uid":82640,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"你屌林鄭老母架嘛<br />\n<br />\n想出黎搶何君堯戰尾票<br />\n唔好俾機會佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b962bd8c97d939ea6ed7bcac7841e6f08fc4650f","tid":136809